{"tid":1151251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"母親節一定要送禮物俾母親？","createTime":"2019-05-12T12:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T12:59:00.000Z","uid":156806,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"908563bf6d8fdcc4551392de1c60c72f86b53345","tid":1151251,"uid":156806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:20:28.000Z","msg":"正評：不送<br />\n負評：送<br />\n<br />\n首先，我有send母親節快樂俾我啊媽。<br />\n但俾女朋友話我小氣，幼稚，禮物都唔送。<br />\n第時肯定都唔會送俾佢（女朋友）<br />\n咁我係出國讀書，母親在香港，送唔到。<br />\n佢叫我上網送野運返香港俾我啊媽。<br />\n但我覺得無必要，有心意就夠。<br />\n跟手就嬲左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家節日咁商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013605ea38d563c47bb5f8a3317b925b04f47f7f","tid":1151251,"uid":156806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d0a2ec0f097601ad8638acc9bfaccb2248daa35","tid":1151251,"uid":156806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"負評都講下原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a37a732ae34014d6300244c46f012ff2897a90d","tid":1151251,"uid":247905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"應該母親送俾子女<br />\n母親之所以做到母親係因為有子女<br />\n應該母親感激子女"},{"pid":"340d6024ed8efde2023a3791b5565f93d23d4618","tid":1151251,"uid":147952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"簡單，其實可以咁諗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">揾錢um住佢地把口</span>"},{"pid":"63cc99c597d0bddd3be194c24af065c212493e16","tid":1151251,"uid":156806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"錢都未搵到個，都唔知送咩俾老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />